<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 02:26:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-2257-d21c-abae-76ffa5890000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:42:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-2257-d21c-abae-76ffa5890000</guid></item><item><title>“即使在整个战争中，我实际上更喜欢以色列人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-01/ty-article/.highlight/even-within-this-whole-war-i-actually-like-israelis-more/0000018c-2248-dc03-a9ec-3e7b1af00000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名低音提琴手解释了在如此痛苦的时刻演奏音乐的感觉，一名酒店工作人员离开一个战区前往另一个战区</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-01/ty-article/.highlight/even-within-this-whole-war-i-actually-like-israelis-more/0000018c-2248-dc03-a9ec-3e7b1af00000</guid></item><item><title>红十字会必须走</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-red-cross-must-go/0000018c-21c7-d9ef-abcd-3fe7a3380000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:12:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-red-cross-must-go/0000018c-21c7-d9ef-abcd-3fe7a3380000</guid></item><item><title>我在与哈马斯的战争中失去了我的儿子。武力和暴力不是解决问题的办法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-lost-my-son-to-the-war-with-hamas-force-and-violence-arent-the-solution/0000018c-21f1-dc03-a9ec-3dfb54630000</link><description>七百万犹太人可以用暴力永远统治数百万巴勒斯坦人，而不会付出失去民主的高昂代价——或者对我来说，失去我心爱的第一个孩子——的想法是一种幻想。 10月7日破灭的幻想</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-lost-my-son-to-the-war-with-hamas-force-and-violence-arent-the-solution/0000018c-21f1-dc03-a9ec-3dfb54630000</guid></item><item><title>可以挽救内塔尼亚胡遗产的一举一动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-one-move-that-can-save-netanyahus-legacy/0000018c-21e1-da36-a1de-67e7a2fc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 21:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-one-move-that-can-save-netanyahus-legacy/0000018c-21e1-da36-a1de-67e7a2fc0000</guid></item><item><title>否认哈马斯的暴行是其对以色列进行心理虐待的又一个阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-of-hamas-atrocities-is-another-stage-in-its-psychological-abuse/0000018c-21e1-d9ef-abcd-3fe19f370000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 21:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-of-hamas-atrocities-is-another-stage-in-its-psychological-abuse/0000018c-21e1-d9ef-abcd-3fe19f370000</guid></item><item><title>停止本-格维尔枪支表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/stop-the-ben-gvir-gun-show/0000018c-21e1-dc03-a9ec-3dfba0030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 21:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/stop-the-ben-gvir-gun-show/0000018c-21e1-dc03-a9ec-3dfba0030000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的部门偷工减料向以色列人发放持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-cuts-corners-to-issue-gun-permits-to-israelis/0000018c-21be-d21c-abae-77beee350000</link><description>以色列一名高级安全官员表示，这种行为会酿成灾难。 “他们像分发糖果一样分发枪支。枪支许可证不是儿童游戏。该部几乎没有监督”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-cuts-corners-to-issue-gun-permits-to-israelis/0000018c-21be-d21c-abae-77beee350000</guid></item><item><title>一次又一次的证词揭露了哈马斯强奸以色列妇女活动的范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-campaign-of-rape-against-israeli-women-is-revealed-testimony-after-testimony/0000018c-2144-da36-a1de-6767dac90000</link><description>Cochav Elkayam-Levy 博士和她的民事委员会收集的证据汇总，呈现出一幅不容置疑的可怕景象：10 月 7 日，哈马斯恐怖分子有系统地实施了强奸和性虐待行为。然而她发现，国外并不急于承认这一点</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-campaign-of-rape-against-israeli-women-is-revealed-testimony-after-testimony/0000018c-2144-da36-a1de-6767dac90000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷恐怖袭击引发加沙战斗蔓延的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/the-jerusalem-terror-attack-raises-concerns-about-the-spillover-of-fighting-from-gaza/0000018c-208a-d9ef-abcd-3eab91230000</link><description>耶路撒冷发生的致命恐怖袭击为以色列国家安全部长提供了推动其枪支分配政策的弹药，从而强化了最终鼓励极端分子的反馈循环</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:15:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/the-jerusalem-terror-attack-raises-concerns-about-the-spillover-of-fighting-from-gaza/0000018c-208a-d9ef-abcd-3eab91230000</guid></item><item><title>杀害耶路撒冷恐怖分子的以色列士兵射杀平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-who-killed-jerusalem-terrorists-shoot-and-wound-civilian/0000018c-216f-d9ef-abcd-3f6fb6a30000</link><description>在社交媒体上发布的耶路撒冷公交车站枪击事件的视频中，尤瓦尔·多伦·卡斯特尔曼举起双手，恳求以色列士兵不要开枪，随后他中弹倒地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 19:33:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-who-killed-jerusalem-terrorists-shoot-and-wound-civilian/0000018c-216f-d9ef-abcd-3f6fb6a30000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列妇女从哈马斯的囚禁中获释，另外八名妇女将在几小时后获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-women-freed-from-hamas-captivity-eight-more-set-to-be-released-hours-later/0000018c-2148-dc03-a9ec-3d7b21800000</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，40 岁的阿米特·苏萨纳 (Amit Soussana) 和 21 岁的以色列-法国双重国籍的米亚·谢姆 (Mia Schem) 比其他人更早获释，因为人质被关押在加沙各地的不同地点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 18:13:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-women-freed-from-hamas-captivity-eight-more-set-to-be-released-hours-later/0000018c-2148-dc03-a9ec-3d7b21800000</guid></item><item><title>Ofir Tzarfati 于 10 月 7 日在 Nova 音乐节上被绑架，被发现死于加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ofir-tzarfati-abducted-during-the-rave-was-found-dead-in-gaza/0000018c-210d-dc03-a9ec-3d7f5ac90000</link><description>以色列军队在加沙地带与哈马斯作战时发现了他的尸体，并将其归还给以色列。同样在周四，据信也被哈马斯囚禁的阿维夫·阿齐利 (Aviv Atzili) 的家人获悉他的死讯。他的伴侣利亚特于周三从哈马斯的囚禁中获释</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 17:50:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ofir-tzarfati-abducted-during-the-rave-was-found-dead-in-gaza/0000018c-210d-dc03-a9ec-3d7f5ac90000</guid></item><item><title>为什么哈马斯杀手援引上帝的名字，而不是解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/why-hamas-killers-invoked-gods-name-not-the-liberation-of-palestine/0000018c-2136-d21c-abae-77be854e0000</link><description>如果有人想找到解决以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的办法，接受这样一个事实：这首先是一场宗教民族主义冲突 — — 而不是从西方校园引进的某种基于种族和定居者殖民的人为概念 — — 将是一个绝佳的选择开始</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 17:38:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/why-hamas-killers-invoked-gods-name-not-the-liberation-of-palestine/0000018c-2136-d21c-abae-77be854e0000</guid></item><item><title>震惊世界的选举结果：反穆斯林极右翼如何在荷兰取得胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-elections-that-shook-the-world-how-the-anti-muslim-far-right-won-the-netherlands/0000018c-2019-d9ef-abcd-3e3923060000</link><description>荷兰政治专家警告说，当中右翼政党寻求在极右翼问题上竞争时，他们只能成功地使极端分子合法化并为他们打开权力之门</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 17:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-elections-that-shook-the-world-how-the-anti-muslim-far-right-won-the-netherlands/0000018c-2019-d9ef-abcd-3e3923060000</guid></item><item><title>英雄与恶棍：为什么亨利·基辛格对犹太人和以色列人来说是一个如此矛盾的人物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/hero-and-villain-why-henry-kissinger-was-such-an-ambivalent-figure-for-jews-and-israelis/0000018c-209b-dc03-a9ec-3cfb59cc0000</link><description>基辛格是一名来自纳粹德国的儿童难民，后来成为 20 世纪最有影响力的犹太人物之一。在对尼克松反犹太主义的绥靖和中东穿梭外交的发明之间，他作为美国人和犹太人都留下了有争议的遗产</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/hero-and-villain-why-henry-kissinger-was-such-an-ambivalent-figure-for-jews-and-israelis/0000018c-209b-dc03-a9ec-3cfb59cc0000</guid></item><item><title>国家预算传奇证明内塔尼亚胡并没有意识到他的政府已经注定失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/state-budget-approval-saga-proves-netanyahu-doesnt-get-that-his-government-is-doomed/0000018c-20aa-da36-a1de-67af6b3e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在战时违背公众情绪，贿赂极端正统联盟伙伴来拯救政府，他依赖于他的主要竞争对手、战时内阁成员本尼·甘茨——他正在等待离开政府并开始行动的合适时机。驱逐他的过程</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/state-budget-approval-saga-proves-netanyahu-doesnt-get-that-his-government-is-doomed/0000018c-20aa-da36-a1de-67af6b3e0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列孕妇被刺死；警方逮捕两名家庭成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/pregnant-arab-israeli-woman-stabbed-to-death-police-arrest-two-family-members/0000018c-20cd-dc03-a9ec-3cffd7ac0000</link><description>正值妊娠末期的阿雅·阿布·哈贾吉 (Aya Abu Hajjaj) 被送往医院进行紧急剖腹产，试图挽救婴儿，但最终医护人员不得不宣布两人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:18:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/pregnant-arab-israeli-woman-stabbed-to-death-police-arrest-two-family-members/0000018c-20cd-dc03-a9ec-3cffd7ac0000</guid></item><item><title>纳莱迪人真的埋葬了死者吗？现在有办法可以查到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/did-homo-naledi-really-bury-its-dead-now-there-are-ways-to-find-out/0000018c-2080-d9ef-abcd-3ea10b130000</link><description>一篇新论文提出了利用地球科学技术来减少考古发现的不确定性的案例，例如是否有小脑人类在墙壁上雕刻并埋葬了死者</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/did-homo-naledi-really-bury-its-dead-now-there-are-ways-to-find-out/0000018c-2080-d9ef-abcd-3ea10b130000</guid></item><item><title>闭嘴跳舞：特拉维夫的俱乐部场景因不关心政治而付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/our-parties-contributed-to-the-deafening-whitewashing-of-the-state-of-israel/0000018c-15a0-dd03-a7ff-bfb85afb0000</link><description>自 2002 年“狂欢反对占领”以来，以色列的夜生活场景和政治活动之间就没有任何联系。现在我们在世界舞台上为此付出了沉重的代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/our-parties-contributed-to-the-deafening-whitewashing-of-the-state-of-israel/0000018c-15a0-dd03-a7ff-bfb85afb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>